---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Our Supervisors | Brenkley Doctoral College" description="Meet the Brenkley Doctoral College supervisory team — experienced academics and practitioner-scholars who guide doctoral researchers to completion.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-surface border-b border-border py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="section-label mb-4">The Team</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Our Supervisors</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">Brenkley Doctoral College supervisors are practitioner-scholars — academics with deep professional experience who understand the distinctive challenges and opportunities of practitioner research. They bring intellectual rigour, professional insight, and genuine commitment to their researchers.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Supervisors Grid -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

        <!-- Stanley Oliver -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-1">Prof. Stanley Oliver</h2>
            <p class="text-accent font-medium mb-3">Principal</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
              <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Management Strategy</span>
              <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Mixed Methods</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-4">Stanley leads Brenkley Doctoral College's strategic direction and is an active doctoral supervisor specialising in management strategy, organisational leadership, and executive decision-making. He brings over two decades of experience in executive education and practitioner research methodology.</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-muted mb-6">
            <span><strong class="text-foreground">6</strong> active researchers</span>
            <span>&bull;</span>
            <span>Mixed methods</span>
            <span>&bull;</span>
            <span>Management, Strategy</span>
          </div>
          <a href="/supervisors/stanley-oliver" class="btn-primary">View profile</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Zahra Salimi -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-1">Dr. Zahra Salimi</h2>
            <p class="text-accent font-medium mb-3">Academic Lead for Research &amp; Enterprise</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
              <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Education Leadership</span>
              <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Qualitative</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-4">Zahra oversees academic quality across all Brenkley Doctoral College programmes and supervises researchers in education leadership, policy, and practitioner-researcher identity. A specialist in qualitative inquiry, she has published widely on insider research ethics and the experience of professional doctorates.</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-muted mb-6">
            <span><strong class="text-foreground">4</strong> active researchers</span>
            <span>&bull;</span>
            <span>Qualitative</span>
            <span>&bull;</span>
            <span>Education, Policy</span>
          </div>
          <a href="/supervisors/zahra-salimi" class="btn-primary">View profile</a>
        </div>


        <!-- Liz Blower -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-1">Dr. Liz Blower</h2>
            <p class="text-accent font-medium mb-3">Academic Lead for Operations &amp; Finance</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
              <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Student Wellbeing</span>
              <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Qualitative</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-4">Liz leads pastoral support and student experience across Brenkley Doctoral College, ensuring every researcher has the support they need to thrive. She supervises researchers in professional education, doctoral wellbeing, and qualitative methodologies. Her research focuses on identity and wellbeing in professional doctoral study.</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-muted mb-6">
            <span><strong class="text-foreground">3</strong> active researchers</span>
            <span>&bull;</span>
            <span>Qualitative</span>
            <span>&bull;</span>
            <span>Wellbeing, Education</span>
          </div>
          <a href="/supervisors/liz-blower" class="btn-primary">View profile</a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Adjunct Faculty -->
  <section class="border-t border-border py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <p class="section-label mb-3">Partner Institutions</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Adjunct Faculty</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

        <!-- Paul G. Oliver -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-1">Dr Paul G. Oliver</h2>
            <p class="text-accent font-medium mb-3 text-sm">Lecturer in Digital Innovation and Entrepreneurship, Edinburgh Napier University</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
              <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Digital Innovation</span>
              <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Responsible AI</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-4">Specialises in digital transformation, entrepreneurship and innovation within the creative industries, with particular expertise in platformisation, algorithmic bias, data governance, and intellectual property management.</p>
          <a href="/supervisors/adjunct-faculty" class="btn-primary">View profile</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Xiaoling Wu -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-1">Dr Xiaoling Wu</h2>
            <p class="text-accent font-medium mb-3 text-sm">Lecturer, Business School, Edinburgh Napier University</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
              <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Digital Transformation</span>
              <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Data Governance</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-4">Specialises in entrepreneurship, innovation, digital transformation and data governance, with a focus on responsible AI and digital innovation ecosystems within public and private sector organisations.</p>
          <a href="/supervisors/adjunct-faculty" class="btn-primary">View profile</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Premnath K. Narayanan -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-1">Dr Premnath K. Narayanan</h2>
            <p class="text-accent font-medium mb-3 text-sm">Researcher, Educator and Technology Leader</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
              <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Artificial Intelligence</span>
              <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Machine Learning</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-4">Specialises in artificial intelligence, machine learning, digital transformation and advanced computing, with particular expertise in LLMs, retrieval-augmented generation, and responsible AI.</p>
          <a href="/supervisors/adjunct-faculty" class="btn-primary">View profile</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Stefanie Schuster -->
        <div class="card">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-1">Dr Stefanie Schuster</h2>
            <p class="text-accent font-medium mb-3 text-sm">Researcher and Industry Practitioner</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
              <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Organisational Development</span>
              <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Applied Research</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-4">Brings extensive practitioner leadership experience into research, supervision and professional development, with interests in organisational leadership, innovation, and strategic management.</p>
          <a href="/supervisors/adjunct-faculty" class="btn-primary">View profile</a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Supervision approach -->
  <section class="bg-surface border-y border-border py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <p class="section-label mb-3">How We Supervise</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Our Supervisory Approach</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3">Partnership, Not Direction</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">We do not believe supervisors should direct doctoral researchers towards predetermined conclusions. Our role is to challenge your thinking, extend your reading, strengthen your methodology, and ensure your work meets the highest standards — while keeping you in the driving seat of your own research.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3">Regular, Structured Meetings</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">All Brenkley Doctoral College researchers have a minimum of eight supervision meetings per year, with meetings minuted on our online platform. You will never wonder where you stand — your progress, your next steps, and your development targets are always clearly recorded and visible.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-3">Expert Matching</h3>
          <p class="text-muted text-sm">Supervisor matching is taken seriously at Brenkley Doctoral College. Before you enrol, the Director of Doctoral Studies leads a careful process to identify the supervisor whose expertise and working style best fit your research. The match can be reviewed if either party feels a change is needed.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Interested in working with us?</h2>
      <p class="text-muted mb-8">The first step is a conversation. Book a no-obligation discussion with our admissions team to talk about your research interests and find the right supervisory match.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap">
        <a href="/apply" class="btn-primary">Apply now</a>
        <a href="/connect" class="btn-outline">Book a conversation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
